data.description: GET A 3.265% INTEREST RATE ON THIS HOUSE! You'll have to qualify with the current lender for this assumable loan! NEARLY NEW and FULL of upgrades! If you're even considering buying a new home in Deer Crest you've got to do yourself a favor and see this beauty. Spacious and airy, this floor plan offers something for everyone with a flex space downstairs (currently used as an office), big living room adjacent to the dining area & open kitchen - this is a *fantastic* place to gather & entertain! Head upstairs to see the amply-sized loft/game room and all 3 bedrooms. The owners' suite features a full bath with double vanities and a luxurious tiled shower. Just minutes from shopping, IH-35, and all that New Braunfels has to offer. Schedule your showing today!
